  "texts": [
    "Looking at all these \"omics\" together can give us a more complete picture of how drugs work together and interact at the molecular level, helping identify the best combinations.",
    "Artificial intelligence, especially deep learning, will also play a bigger role.",
    "These advanced algorithms excel at finding complex patterns in data, which is perfect for capturing the nonlinear relationships inside our bodies.",
    "This should lead to more accurate predictions of synergistic drug effects.",
    "of different classifiers using a synergy score [-5, 5] range."
  ]
